   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>On Pauni 7.;Has brought Komon, through Ptollas son of Apollonios, for the 14th indiction, of the villagers of Karanis, two-hundred and forty litrai of chaff, = 240 litrai, only. I, Paulos, have signed.</ab>
